content.text: The database has `NCESSchool` in the `schools` table and `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` in the `frpm` table. Let me query the top enrollments by NCES school ID.

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT s.NCESSchool, f.\"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\", f.\"School Name\" FROM frpm f JOIN schools s ON f.CDSCode = s.CDSCode WHERE s.NCESSchool IS NOT NULL ORDER BY f.\"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\" DESC LIMIT 10;"
